query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('bash',
'drivers',
'mount',
'package-management',
'permissions',
'scripts',
'software-installation',
'unity',
'updates')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Caucus',
'Critic',
'Enthusiast',
'Favorite Question',
'Good Answer',
'Organizer',
'Quorum')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
